    "content": "<div class=\"noinclude\"><span class=\"breadcrumbs xulRefAttr_breadcrumbs\">Â« <a href=\"/en-US/docs/XUL/XUL_Reference\">XUL Reference home</a></span></div>\n\n<dl>\n <dt><code id=\"a-menuitem.name\"><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XUL/Attribute/menuitem.name\">name</a></code></dt>\n <dd>Type: <em>string name</em></dd>\n <dd>Radio <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XUL/menuitem\" title=\"menuitem\">menuitem</a></code>s with the same name as put into a group. Only one <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Tech/XUL/menuitem\" title=\"menuitem\">menuitem</a></code> in each radio group can be checked at a time.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<div class=\"noinclude\">\n<h3 id=\"Example\" name=\"Example\">Example</h3>\n\n<pre>&lt;toolbox&gt;\n  &lt;menubar id=\"planets-menubar\"&gt;\n    &lt;menu id=\"planet-menu\" label=\"Planet\"&gt;\n      &lt;menupopup&gt;\n        &lt;menuitem id=\"jupiter\" label=\"Jupiter\" type=\"radio\" name=\"planet\"/&gt;\n        &lt;menuitem id=\"saturn\" label=\"Saturn\" type=\"radio\" name=\"planet\" checked=\"true\"/&gt;\n        &lt;menuitem id=\"uranus\" label=\"Uranus\" type=\"radio\" name=\"planet\"/&gt;\n      &lt;/menupopup&gt;\n    &lt;/menu&gt;\n  &lt;/menubar&gt;\n&lt;/toolbox&gt;\n</pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"See_also\" name=\"See_also\">See also</h3>\n\n<p><a href=\"/en/XUL/Attribute/name\" title=\"en/XUL/Attribute/name\">name</a> and <a href=\"/en/XUL_Tutorial/More_Menu_Features#Adding_Checkmarks_to_Menus\" title=\"en/XUL_Tutorial/More_Menu_Features#Adding_Checkmarks_to_Menus\">menus in the XUL Tutorial</a></p>\n</div>",
